<a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s7.sinaimg.cn/orignal/49bb80ccta95f7b6f8776" TARGET="_blank"><img HEIGHT="400" SRC="http://s7.sinaimg.cn/middle/49bb80ccta95f7b6f8776&amp;690" WIDTH="600" NAME="image_operate_3141312127707796" /></A><br />
<br /></P>
<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;再见了，缪风燕。</P>
<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
